Package: deadlywish
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Sand battle game
 Four player arena battle game created in C ++ by brazilian university students at the FGA engineering campus, the goal of the game is to defeat the enemy by attacking their tower, the last tower that is standing will be the winner.
